%% SCENARIO 7: Delete Post
%% =======================

sequenceDiagram
    title Scenario 7: Delete Post

    actor User
    participant Frontend as Frontend (React)
    participant APIGateway as API Gateway
    participant PostsService as Posts Service
    participant Database as Database

    User->>Frontend: 1. Open post details
    Frontend->>APIGateway: 2. GET /posts/{postID}
    APIGateway->>PostsService: 3. GetPost(postID, userID)
    PostsService->>Database: 4. SELECT Post WHERE id = postID
    Database-->>PostsService: 5. Post {userID, content, mediaURLs}
    PostsService-->>APIGateway: 6. PostResponse
    APIGateway-->>Frontend: 7. 200 OK {post}
    Frontend-->>User: 8. Display post content

    User->>Frontend: 9. Click delete button
    Frontend->>Frontend: 10. Show confirmation dialog

    User->>Frontend: 11. Confirm delete
    Frontend->>APIGateway: 12. DELETE /posts/{postID}
    APIGateway->>PostsService: 13. DeletePost(postID, userID)
    PostsService->>Database: 14. SELECT Post WHERE id = postID
    Database-->>PostsService: 15. Post {userID}
    PostsService->>PostsService: 16. Check ownership
    PostsService->>Database: 17. DELETE Post WHERE id = postID
    Database-->>PostsService: 18. OK
    PostsService-->>APIGateway: 19. {success}
    APIGateway-->>Frontend: 20. 200 OK
    Frontend-->>User: 21. Success: Post deleted!

    Frontend->>Frontend: 22. Redirect to feed
    Frontend-->>User: 23. Show updated feed

